Title: Loved the wood-fired pizza and mocktails at the Parel branch — worth the walk from the station!
Feedback: Visited the Parel outlet with friends last weekend. Great ambience, perfectly baked pizzas, and refreshing cocktails. Slightly pricey but worth it.

Title: Airoli branch has great pizzas but the location is a bit hard to find
Feedback: Tucked away from the main area but pizzas are delicious. Jain Margherita was nice. Needs better signage.

Title: Parel outlet rocks for meat lovers, cocktails were the cherry on top!
Feedback: Perfect spot for non-veg pizza lovers. Amazing pepperoni pizza, great crowd, bit busy but fun.

Title: Jain pizzas were average, but service and ambience made up for it
Feedback: Jain Farmhouse Pizza was okay. Ambience and service were good though. Great for mixed food groups.

Title: Great pizza variety at Airoli, but please add vegan burgers too!
Feedback: Loved pizzas but wish there were vegan burgers too. Friendly staff, cozy setup.

Title: Best pizza crust in Mumbai! The Parel branch is my new go-to
Feedback: Crispy crust, juicy toppings, and smooth cocktails. Excellent vibe. Must visit!

Title: Average taste at Airoli, nothing special except the ambience
Feedback: Pizzas lacked flavor, cocktails good. Ambience nice, service slow.

Title: Excellent combo of pizza and cocktails — totally worth visiting again!
Feedback: Great music, lovely food, awesome cocktails. Perfect post-work hangout!

Title: Great place for family dining — even Jain options available!
Feedback: Jain pizzas tasty, clean space, great service. Good for families.

Title: Cocktails and cheesy pizzas at Parel — a perfect night out spot!
Feedback: Fun vibe, cheesy pizza, loud music though. Still enjoyable.

Title: Disappointed with delayed service at Airoli, though pizza tasted fine
Feedback: Tasty pizza but service was painfully slow. Needs better management.

Title: Parel branch ambience top-notch, but cocktails overpriced
Feedback: Pizzas great, cocktails too costly. Ambience superb.

Title: Tried vegan pizza at Airoli, sadly bland and underwhelming
Feedback: Vegan options need improvement. Crust good, flavor missing.

Title: A pizza lover’s dream at Parel – excellent service and flavors
Feedback: Loved Chicken Fiesta, amazing service, clean setup. Highly recommended.

Title: Great for groups but not ideal for couples seeking quiet time
Feedback: Too noisy for dates, but food and drinks are nice.

Title: Staff messed up our order at Airoli, not a pleasant visit
Feedback: Wrong pizza delivered twice, though they apologized. Long wait.

Title: Tasty non-veg pizzas at Parel, but skip the burgers
Feedback: Non-veg pizza awesome, burger dry. Stick to pizzas!

Title: Cozy Airoli outlet, limited options but calm and relaxing
Feedback: Quiet atmosphere, limited menu but fresh food. Ideal for families.

Title: Horrible experience at Parel — loud music, warm drinks, soggy crust
Feedback: Crowded, soggy pizza, poor service. Disappointing.

Title: Perfect hangout spot with friends — pizza, cocktails, and fun vibes!
Feedback: Amazing vibe, delicious pizza, fun place for parties.

Title: Loved the Airoli outlet for its calm vibe and tasty pizzas
Feedback: Went with family, loved the service and taste. Kids enjoyed the cheese burst pizza. Peaceful spot away from crowds.

Title: Too loud at Parel branch but food was decent
Feedback: Music too loud for conversations, but the BBQ chicken pizza was amazing. Cocktails average.

Title: Great pizzas at Airoli but staff seemed uninterested
Feedback: Food was good but the waiters looked distracted. Still, the veg supreme pizza was excellent.

Title: Parel outlet is a foodie’s paradise — but pricey
Feedback: Loved the peri-peri chicken pizza and sangria. Just wish the prices were a bit lower.

Title: Airoli branch good for families but limited Jain options
Feedback: Nice environment for families, but only two Jain pizzas available. Taste was decent though.

Title: Fantastic cocktails and thin-crust pizzas at Parel
Feedback: The thin-crust pizza was perfection! Cocktails top-notch. Loved the interiors too.

Title: Decent Airoli outlet, but location hard to spot
Feedback: Good pizza and calm setting. Needs better visibility from main road though.

Title: Burger lover disappointed — but pizza saved the day!
Feedback: No vegan or Jain burgers, but the pizza made up for it. Parel staff very friendly.

Title: Airoli branch too quiet, felt lifeless but good food
Feedback: Very calm place, maybe too quiet. Pizza was fresh and tasty though.

Title: Loved every bit of the Parel branch — from crust to cocktails!
Feedback: Top-notch food, great ambience, fun evening. Definitely coming back!
